> \n</div></div>\n<div style=\"width: 630px; float: left; padding-bottom: 11px; padding-top: 11px; padding-left: 11px; margin-left: 20px; padding-right: 11px\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    <div class=\"zbtys\">个人简介</div>\n    <div class=\"znrys\">\n        <p></p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; &nbsp;主要从事构造地质学、微观构造、岩石流变学与盆地构造研究与教学工作。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; &nbsp;基于地质和岩石物性数据，精细解析和模拟分析地壳各构造层变形与构造、断裂与盆地体系几何学、运动学、裂缝机制、水</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">-</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family: 宋体\">岩作用过程与动力、微米</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">-</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family: 宋体\">纳米级储层物性及其成矿</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">-</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family: 宋体\">成藏评价。研究主要聚焦喜马拉雅构造、滇西新生代陆内断裂体系演化、祁连山冲断带及河西走廊盆地构造、中国东部中</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">-</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family: 宋体\">新生代深部岩石圈演化的浅部构造与沉积响应等。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">先后承担国家自然科学基金</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">4</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">项（青年基金</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">1</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">项、面上基金</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">2</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">项、优秀青年基金</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">1</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">项），国家油气重大专项课题</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">，国家重点研发计划课题、中国地震局行业专项</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">（活动断裂填图），国家</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">973</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">课题（青年</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">973</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">项目），参加青藏高原第二次科学考察（专题联络人）等</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">。发表学术论文五十余篇，主要发表在</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">Journal of Structural Geology, Tectonics, Tectonophysics, GRL，G3, Science China (Earth Sciences)</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">等学术期刊。是</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">JSG</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">JGR-s</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">Tectonics</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">Tectonophysics</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">Science China (Earth Sciences)</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">、岩石学报、地质学报等学术期刊的审稿人。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\"></span><br></p><p></p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"zbtys\">教育经历</div>\n<div class=\"znrys\"> \n  <p>\n  </p><table style=\"width:100%;\">\n    <tbody><tr>\n      <td style=\"width:130px;vertical-align: top;\"> 2002.9 - 2007.7 </td>\n      <td>北京大学\n       <span style=\"color:#fff;background: url(/_ts/zwmb2/images/ico_004.png) right center no-repeat;\">&nbsp;</span>\n        地质学\n       <span style=\"color:#fff;background: url(/_ts/zwmb2/images/ico_004.png) right center no-repeat;\">&nbsp;</span>\n        博士研究生毕业\n       <span style=\"color:#fff;background: url(/_ts/zwmb2/images/ico_004.png) right center no-repeat;\">&nbsp;</span>\n        博士学位  \n         </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody></table>\n  <p></p>\n  \n  <p>\n  </p><table style=\"width:100%;\">\n    <tbody><tr>\n      <td style=\"width:130px;vertical-align: